<item>
            <title>[SPR-2687] Argument binding in pointcut expressions fails with multiple interceptors in chain</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2687</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Binding values in AspectJ style pointcut expressions fails when there are multiple interceptors in the chain. See e.g.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29902:&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29902:&lt;/a&gt; &amp;lt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29902&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29902&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29858:&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29858:&lt;/a&gt; &amp;lt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29858&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=29858&lt;/a&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;
